Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.53,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.70,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold on any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:27.92,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.96,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh great Bettenou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.03,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Bettenou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.03,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Inga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.03,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Detective's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:10.92,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to be \Nlike this, head in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:17.22,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling to escape from \Nthis saturated world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:23.02,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes like whispering sand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.73,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,These circumstances, unchanging
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:29.73,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,gazing out at a dreamless tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:36.82,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna say goodbye to the \Nconfusion of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:42.24,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I try reaching out, as if to resist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:47.96,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,We cry millions of times \Nand then get born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.17,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with these red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.38,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,to that pictured future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:59.93,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Come here right by me, \NI'm clapping my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.01,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:06.43,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Strain my eyes in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:12.02,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see anything, don't know \Nanything, but I'll still go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:18.40,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,To the place of shining \Nlight in which you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.99,Episode Num,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.99,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Just Searching
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.99,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by "Sneering Demon" and "Red Trap" from Ango Sakaguchi's\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Detective Stories)\Nand from "I Give Reason"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:27.50,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Kaishou wasn't on any \Ncameras at the TV station...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:32.38,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Diet Member \NKuramitsu had us say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.92,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}AD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.92,Name Sub,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Motoyama's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:34.92,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,This was delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.88,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Kaishou Rinroku is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.38,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyama Minami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.38,Name Sub,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Television Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.93,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shijurou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.93,Name Sub,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:43.39,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is what my father said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.93,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Rie, I was definitely at home, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.10,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must we go over this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.56,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.94,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Kaishou Rie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.94,Name Sub,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Daughter of Kaishou Rinroku, Lives at Home
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.94,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Family Maid (Head Maid)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.94,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Family Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.94,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:55.52,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Was this delivered to you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:03:00.57,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Did the hospital provide Kaishou \NRinroku's DNA to verify his remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:02.70,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.62,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,She did, from my father's brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.95,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:11.62,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,If solar power generation is \Nnationalized, Kaishou Rinroku won't be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:16.21,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,profit from the electric utility \Nindustry that he introduced to the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.80,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Nationalize Solar Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.80,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,But he's passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.30,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that divine retribution?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.85,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Our generation can create a smart grid \Nenvironment and solar power plants,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.85,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Kuramitsu Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.85,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}New Diet Member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:30.06,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,making Japan a great nation, the \Nworld's leader in renewable energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.81,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:38.98,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's possible to accept \Nthe invitation, but just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.99,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,But it makes me wonder who \Nwould pull a prank like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.32,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku's ghost, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.46,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.29,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to stop her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.71,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Your father has definitely passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.71,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Hayami Seigen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.71,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Director of the Security Bureau \NMetropolitan Police Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.71,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Koyama Izumi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.71,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Public Prosecutor\N Joint Coordinating Dept.\N Public Prosecutor's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:01.72,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to know who \Nis using his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.18,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,This is in extremely poor taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.60,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,You always see it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.77,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fuwa Jujirou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.60,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Victims summoned to the\N scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.69,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't for a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.60,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,I was called here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.27,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,"An invitation to a party,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.15,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Mihara Yasutarou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.15,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Member of the Public Security Force,\NCommanded by Mizuno
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.28,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,in which the real person behind \Nthe bombing will be rooted out."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.20,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.37,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Did you set this up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.53,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,You too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.95,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.95,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all take our seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.04,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The party is going to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.50,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.00,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Defeated Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.84,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't enough you drove Chairman \NKaishou to commit suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.13,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now this farce...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I was called here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:49.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a crime \Nis going to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.64,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And a major crime at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.89,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,What "major crime"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.60,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Fuwa Jujirou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.60,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Entrepreneur
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:57.06,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou tried to murder us, and when \Nhe was exposed, he killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.44,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,The crimes are over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.99,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.24,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What does my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:14.25,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what does the organizer \Nof this party want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.21,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. But how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:21.30,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge against the person \Nwho framed Kaishou Rinroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.55,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.09,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are we supposed to kill each \Nother with these weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.30,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,until the real criminal is found?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.68,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you should \Nbe the first one to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.31,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I admit that my deductions were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.73,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I gracefully admit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.94,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:42.52,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,When the explosion happened here, \Nthe real Mr. Kaishou was at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,while the one who showed up at \Nthe TV station was an impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.20,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It was all done through \Nthe power of Bettenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.24,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.53,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's what I was {\i1}made{\i0} to figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:53.49,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yuuki Shinjurou will definitely \Ndeduce the presence of Bettenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.62,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Since he is a great detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.29,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou obtained Bettenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.96,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,To make me think that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.80,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou was purposely paraded in \Nfront of a member of his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that this family member has \Na scrupulously honest personality
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,was part of the calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.72,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.76,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying my deductions \Nwere wrong before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.89,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kaishou Rinroku \Nwas at the TV studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.69,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The Kaishou you witnessed at \Nhome was the {\i1}real{\i0} mastermind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.56,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,camouflaged by Bettenou \Nto look like Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.49,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this "Bettenou" \Nyou keep bringing up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.78,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as powerful hypnotism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.20,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have proof that the Chairman \NKaishou at the TV station is the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.91,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Video from the surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:39.62,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If the Kaishou who showed up at the TV \Nstation was a Bettenou-empowered poser,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:42.42,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to \Nsee him on video days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.09,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But I did see him. Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.01,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't taken the train for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.72,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,that I didn't know where \Nto make the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.80,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,We dropped him off at the \NTV station yesterday too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.80,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,but to think this could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.10,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you explained that the \Ncontradiction between the two statements
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.35,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,was proof that Mr. Kaishou \N{\i1}wasn't{\i0} at the TV station!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.52,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.69,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,One of them was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:07.40,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fuwa, you must have heard what \NChairman Kaishou said then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.82,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, he said \Nsomething about taking the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:14.12,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then Mizuno was the one that was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:17.95,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But why would Mizuno tell a lie that \Nwould incriminate Chairman Kaishou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.42,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mizuno was with Full Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.96,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno had information that he \Nshould've had no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.47,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Unusually enough, you were successful \Nwith Mr. Yajima's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Information about a case \Nthat he could've known about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:34.30,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,only if he had access to the prosecutor \Nor Kaishou's private records.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.59,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But don't let it go to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:40.56,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,There was a rumor that Commander \NMizuno also demanded a full access key
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.35,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,to major companies, claiming \Nit was necessary for security.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.90,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Was Mr. Mizuno the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.07,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Missile...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.11,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We had information that a fragment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.86,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,from a shoulder-launched surface-to-air \Nmissile was found here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.99,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,the same kind used by the \NPublic Security Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.99,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been fired from a boat, \Nthere would've been enough distance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.95,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,that even the Self-Defense Force \Nwouldn't have detected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The way you talk makes me think \Nyou've already checked the armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.25,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that Commander Mizuno \Ntook out a missile launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.22,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,We're also left with the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,that a bomb had been set at \Nthe TV station beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:23.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,As for JJ Systems' microwave satellite, \Nit's still in the experimental stages
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and doesn't have the capacity \Nto cause that much destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:30.32,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Then we falsely accused him \Nbased on mistaken data?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.86,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the data that you leaked yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.78,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.95,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say that \NMizuno was the culprit...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.75,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember saying he did it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:47.38,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The Public Security Force may have been \Nable to penetrate corporations' data,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,but authorization is required to have \Naccess to government information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.13,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying Diet Member \NKuramitsu aided Full Circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:58.39,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You hid the fact that you \Nand Mizuno were old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.60,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a member of the \NDiet can get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.23,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,You have no proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.81,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.31,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The handkerchief I lent you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.23,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,My partner brought it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.15,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.44,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into him somewhere \Nand gave it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,My partner had been missing for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.99,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Until Inga appeared at the committee, \Nas if manipulated by something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:28.04,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And the only thing that could possibly \Nmanipulate Inga... is Bettenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:32.46,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you were at the \Nplace where Inga was captured...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And where Bettenou is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.84,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.39,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is a conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.47,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:44.56,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,You made it seem like Kaishou \Nwas alive to frame me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.52,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Gunshots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.10,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.27,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.98,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,He means to attack everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:54.82,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.40,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hayami-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.45,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.58,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really Kaishou's revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.37,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I understand! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.50,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I said bad things about \Nyou because I was tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.04,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold a grudge against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.46,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hold a grudge against anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.93,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.93,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman of JJ Systems
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.94,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.36,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:35.94,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you handle \Na memorial service at your age...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.03,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.24,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.37,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm sorry for \Ncausing so much worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:48.37,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I faked my own death to \Nescape someone's plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:52.92,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,And then I waited for the \Nschemer to make their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.29,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:54.88,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.63,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,he put together this little farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.01,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Defeated Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.43,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,What's your objective, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.51,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just searching for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.22,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to explain your real aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.27,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, this is his partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.81,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not just a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.16,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.78,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, this is not \Na human being, but a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.70,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, the Defeated \NDetective has used this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.67,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,to tear apart human minds \Nwhenever he pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.59,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Today, he's going to \Npay dearly for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.67,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:41.01,Main Dialog,Lady Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me... What is your true goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.05,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.18,Main Dialog,Lady Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.55,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father... That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.72,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:51.02,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,People have no choice but to \Nanswer that monster's question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.56,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Just one question...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:56.40,Main Dialog,Lady Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.48,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Inga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I answered your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.95,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me! Inga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.37,Main Dialog,Lady Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What is it you see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Rain and... Yuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.20,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Only you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:15.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't have to answer \Nany more of your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.96,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I know what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.63,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou is a kami. You \Ncan't resist a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.97,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.68,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to disprove those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.85,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou is no god!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.18,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.43,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that you used that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:34.52,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou makes her master's words \Ninto a semblance of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:38.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't hear the \Nvoice or even see the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.86,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,you can't share in the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.36,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Another thing is she can't turn \Na person into someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.24,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,if that "someone else" is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:49.83,Main Dialog,Lady Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou, you knew, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.71,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Ever since he first got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.75,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,To my eyes, he was just \Nsomeone mimicking Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Hayami Seigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.26,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayami? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.72,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hayami-kun fell to the floor under us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:09.43,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaishou didn't get his hands \Non Bettenou, it had to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.73,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you shot Kazamori as a \Nprecaution against the eye-opening shocks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.02,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,that she used at the prison, \Nbut it didn't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.19,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,What are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.15,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,...you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:23.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that the real Kaishou \NRinroku has been in front of me the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.28,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,so even if a fraudulent Kaishou \Nshows up, my brain won't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.70,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,The real...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.74,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You're stupider than I thought, \NMr. National Police Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.66,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all his responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.21,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Who are you to butt in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.67,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,You can't extract a god out of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:44.13,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,However, by kowtowing to the thing \Nthat is considered to be a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:48.51,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,it is possible to create a god and \Nshove it down the throats of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:52.81,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,Hayami-kun, that's what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.52,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.61,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hayami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.66,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:11.16,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,He used Bettenou's power \Nto impersonate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.33,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Well enough to even fool Rie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.83,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I made it look like I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.63,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,So the person masquerading as \Nme wouldn't be given power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.29,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,I helped the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:26.38,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,That day, it looked like the \NChairman got in the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.47,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,but he actually mixed in with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:35.47,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,For good measure, he disguised himself \Nas a TV station AD and left the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse in the car was the person \Nwho had been brought in to the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.44,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and died the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:46.78,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The DNA matched because some of that \Ncorpse's hair was put on your brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.28,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But that brush was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.20,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,You knew it, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.99,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,That Father was safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.79,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Inga, you still think \NBettenou is a kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:00.96,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,She's a misbegotten soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.92,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Or you could call her \Na soul of mere words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, the statesmen \Nof this country let loose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.47,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,the words "victory" and "kamikaze".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.34,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,They falsely heralded them as \Ngods, and sent them to war...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.06,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,All for the purpose of feigning \Na nonexistent reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:19.18,Main Dialog,Lady Inga,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a soul... then \Nthat's my favorite dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.40,Main Dialog,Lady Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Even one that's misbegotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:16:00.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,By doing this, you figured you \Ncould quickly turn into Kaishou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.27,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and beat the information out of me, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.56,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,You saw through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Full Circle's Mizuno and Kuramitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.15,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,were going to lay out accusations \Nagainst JJ Systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.11,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You, who had acquired Bettenou, \Napproached those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.99,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.37,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku is \Ndriven by self-interest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.79,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,and I wanted to crush him \Nfor the sake of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.21,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.58,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to destroy the \Nnationalization of solar power generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:28.55,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Because {\i1}you{\i0} wanted to \Nbreak into that field!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.72,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,The field I'm going to get \Ninto is solar {\i1}thermal{\i0} energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.01,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's splitting hairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.68,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Your inability to make the distinction \Nbetween the two is your limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.22,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,The age may be coming when \Nwe can provide the technology
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.18,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,to countries with vast \Ndeserts or strong sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.60,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,to build solar thermal power plants \Nthere, and convey the power that's generated
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.48,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,via HVDC transmission,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:52.19,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,so all countries can send microwave \Ntransmissions from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:55.28,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Rely on other \Ncountries for electricity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.07,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.20,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, the borders between \Ncountries will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.75,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of dream I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.89,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You really whetted my appetite, \Ngiving me dribs and drabs like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.20,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can understand Kuramitsu, \Nwho wanted to clip Kaishou's wings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.62,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,because she took a conspiracy \Ntheory seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.58,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But Hayami, what were you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.21,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make this monster \Nask me a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.34,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,That's not nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.13,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, Prosecutor Koyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.97,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Me? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:18:01.18,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. You could never see \Nanyone but Kaishou Rinroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.93,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,To you, Kaishou is just like... a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.81,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to look up to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.31,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:14.44,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,But it was stupid of me \Nto try to become a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.29,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.08,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.16,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:30.42,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Live. Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.55,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:43.76,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what I was going to \Ndo if you didn't notice the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.56,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That was the song from Yonagahime 3+1.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.35,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That member's death was a fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.85,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you weren't dead either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.56,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hardly even call that a deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.07,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And how you knew I was \Ndisguised as an AD as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:19:01.37,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed the location of the real \NAD before I entered the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.99,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.37,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father! The Detective can \Nride with us too, can't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.96,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Well? If you'd like, you can \Njoin us for dinner, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.04,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Father, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.46,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I forgot to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:20.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,About Mizuno, who died \Nin your sham suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:23.97,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Mizuno would have \Ncooperated with your trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:27.60,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,So Mizuno must have been \Ndead before the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.81,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Another reason to stage such a \Nflamboyant suicide as a car bombing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,was to camouflage the \Ncause of Mizuno's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.11,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.40,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:39.78,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:45.37,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that is true, Kaishou, you \Nadmitted that you got rid of Mizuno
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.87,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,before he went public \Nwith any accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.37,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:51.29,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it because Mizuno, \Nwho was with Full Circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.75,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,had gotten {\i1}other{\i0} dirt on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.05,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you talked about \Nsolar thermal power plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.47,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,As compensation for the last war, \Nthe government has made a proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.64,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,to supply technology to other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.52,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You anticipated this far ahead, \Ncooperated during the war, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.27,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Shinjurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.90,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:21.86,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,If all humans were saints and sages, \Nall truths would be exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.74,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,And every just cause, expedient, ideal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.79,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,and lie would no longer \Nbe necessary, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.62,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,But will that day ever come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:38.88,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is better \Nourselves, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.21,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.22,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,People fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.72,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,They unmask their essence, their truth, \Ntheir souls from within them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:50.39,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,People want for beauty; they favor \Nluxury and lust for pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:53.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,yet all the while, and just as \Nstrongly, they know and love what is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.61,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,For each and every evil there \Nis, at the same time, justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.86,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I want to love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.07,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know their beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.86,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,...I expose souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.08,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.37,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to what comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:36.10,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In the pale morning \Nmist, a whispered prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.73,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What did you call me all \Nthe way out here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.06,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I forgot to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.98,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,More bad-mouthing my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:44.11,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm gonna follow this \Ntwisted landscape with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.40,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:46.57,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I haven't shown you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:52.12,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Looking for the "truth", \N"a 'lie' will do" is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.99,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Will you listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:49.78,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:56.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,A woman saved my life once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:22:00.50,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tracing it as if we can see through
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:22:01.09,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,We'd only just met and there was \Nnothing in it for her, but she helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:04.42,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Looking for, beyond words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.59,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,...and she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:06.18,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Inga's body... is hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:08.43,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Like a falling feather
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.80,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to \Nbe together with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.43,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:16.85,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:36.29,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, unravel it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:40.42,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tattered cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:41.54,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Sasa Kazamori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:41.54,Name Sub,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Artificial Intelligence (R.A.I.)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:43.25,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
